up in the finals.\n:{{Color box|limegreen|border=darkgray}} (WIN) The cook won the individual challenge ('''Mystery Box Challenge'''/ '''Skills Test''' or '''Elimination Test''').\n:{{Color box|#959FFD|border=darkgray}} (WIN) The cook was on the winning team in the '''Team Challenge''' and directly advanced to the next round.\n:{{Color box|cornflowerblue|border=darkgray}} (HIGH) The cook was one of the top entries in the individual challenge but didn't win.\n:{{Color box|white|border=darkgray}} (IN) The cook wasn't selected as a top or bottom entry in an individual challenge.\n:{{Color box|palegreen|border=darkgray}} (IN) The cook wasn't selected as a top or bottom entry in a team challenge.\n:{{Color box|yellow|border=darkgray}} (IMM) The cook didn't have to compete in that round of the competition and was safe from elimination.\n:{{Color box|khaki|border=darkgray}} (IMM) The cook was selected by Mystery Box Challenge winner and didn't have to compete in the Elimination Test.\n:{{Color box|mistyrose|border=darkgray}} (PT) The cook was on the losing team in the '''Team Challenge''', competed in the '''Pressure Test''', and advanced.\n:{{Color box|mistyrose|border=darkgray}} (NPT) The cook was on the losing team in the '''Team Challenge''', did not compete in the '''Pressure Test''', and advanced.\n:{{Color box|orange|border=darkgray}} (LOW) The cook was one of the bottom entries in an individual challenge or '''Pressure Test''', and they advanced.\n:{{Color box|purple|border=darkgray}} (LOW) The cook was one of the bottom entries in the '''Team Challenge''' and they advanced.\n:{{Color box|crimson|border=darkgray}} (ELIM) The cook was eliminated from MasterChef.\n\n{{note|1|Note 1}}This contestant was on the winning team but was selected to compete in the elimination test by their team captain.\n\n==Main guest appearances==\n* [[Jennifer Behm]], [[Christine H\u00e0]], [[Shaun O'Neale]] \u2014 Episodes 1 and 2\n* [[Alessandra Ambrosio]] \u2014 Episode 6\n* Gerron Hur